title: Social Studies GED Practice Test 1
intro_text:
Social Studies

Welcome to the Social Studies Practice Test!

This test is 24 questions, which is about half the length of an official High School Equivalency Test. You will not be timed.

The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the High School Equivalency Test.

If you are unsure of an answer, click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later.
